channel.title: I need help making a Runescape Private Server, and a Webclient for it
channel.description:
Hi, for the last month or so I've benn trying to make a RSPS, using every tutorial I can find, but non of them are working... I was wondering if someone could help me by giving me step by step instructions. Or I have a webcam so I could set it at my screen so whoever can see if I'm doing what they tell me right or not.Thanks.
~Death

item.title: I need help making a Runescape Private Server, and a Webclient for it
item.dc:creator: @TheMrDeath TheMrDeath
item.description:
@TheMrDeath wrote:

ravens:

what parts are you having trouble wiht, portforwarding? and use ric’s webclient tutorial u cant go wrong

My problem is… everything I guess firstly I got a client and Server, but when I try to log in it says error connecting to server… Once I get that part working I think I may be able to make a webclient with rs-ps. o r g… But then again, maybe not…

~Death

Nevermind I just found out I can’t portforward…

~Death
